Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.91,0:00:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.28,0:00:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遥  遥怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵音  来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.06,0:00:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且总算是没什么大碍了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过现在还睡着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.14,0:00:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.45,0:00:29.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别哭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.35,0:00:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你哭了  那家伙醒过来的时候会被吓坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道他是身体不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.06,0:00:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办…他大概会讨厌我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.08,0:00:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.82,0:00:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他怎么会因为这些事就讨厌你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.29,0:00:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遥的东西放在教室里没人管
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.31,0:01:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包之类的放着有些危险  我去拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  贵音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.16,0:01:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然还是没脸见他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救了他的是老师吧  请陪在他身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.50,0:01:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真差劲…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.84,0:01:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵音学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.00,0:01:42.00,TIPS-shadow3,,0,0,0,,————————Text-PartA2————————
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文乃？为什么会在学校里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.22,0:01:36.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还没开学哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.04,0:01:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点我还是知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.21,0:01:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.43,0:01:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说是那个？
